'''''Battle Beast''''' is the [[eponymous]] second full-length [[Album (music)|album]] [[Sound recording and reproduction|recorded]] by the [[Heavy metal music|heavy metal]] band [[Battle Beast (band)|Battle Beast]], released in May 2013.<ref name="metal-archives">{{cite web|url=http://www.metal-archives.com/albums/Battle_Beast/Battle_Beast/370817|title=Battle Beast - Battle Beast - Encyclopaedia Metallum: The Metal Archives|publisher=metal-archives.com|accessdate=2014-04-30}}</ref> The album peaked at No. 5 in the Finnish Albums Chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://finnishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Battle+Beast&titel=Battle+Beast&cat=a |title=Battle Beast - Battle Beast (album) |work=Finnishcharts.com |publisher=[[Media Control Charts]] |accessdate=18 August 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729164812/http://finnishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Battle+Beast&titel=Battle+Beast&cat=a |archivedate=29 July 2014 |df= }}</ref>

